These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Cigar: old-henry, baccarat
Job: mechanic, teacher
1. Job:mechanic is in an even position##4
2. Job:teacher == Cigar:baccarat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Cigar   | baccarat | old-henry |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Flower: orchid, balloon-flower
Sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. Sport:sailing is in an odd position##4
2. Flower:balloon-flower is on the left of Flower:orchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | orchid        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: ambient, house
City: venice, nizza
1. City:venice is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:house is on the left of Music-Genre:ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient |
| City   | venice | nizza |

